- INSTALL ADDON FROM REPOSITORY:  https://github.com/zigbee2mqtt/hassio-zigbee2mqtt

- VERIFY THAT YOU PUT THE CORRECT PORT in addon configuration #
Execute the following command in "web and ssh terminal" to find out the correct path:

pi@raspberry:/ $ ls -l /dev/serial/by-id

total 0
lrwxrwxrwx. 1 root root 13 Oct 19 19:26 usb-Texas_Instruments_TI_CC2531_USB_CDC___0X00124B0018ED3DDF-if00 -> ../../ttyACM0

- COFIGURE MQTT: 
mqtt:
  base_topic: zigbee2mqtt
  server: mqtt://192.168.0.2
  user: home
  password: Grushevskogo8a
serial:
  port: /dev/ttyUSB2

- CONFIG ZIGBEE CHANEL:
to avoid interference with wifi on ch1 and ch6 select zigbee ch24 in addon config:
https://www.metageek.com/training/resources/zigbee-wifi-coexistence.html

advanced:
  log_level: warn
  pan_id: 6754
  channel: 24
